Package: simpleweather
Title: Simply retrives weather data
Version: 0.2.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Joseph",
           family = "Marlo",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "joe.marlo.09@gmail.com")
Description: simpleweather is an R package that provides a simple interface to get historical and forecasted weather. It does one thing: retrieve basic weather data for a given latitude, longitude location. No anguish to figure out which data source to use, esoteric weather variable to pick, or weather station to choose.
